# Task Master Agent Integration Template

## **Local-First Strategy**
- Always read `.taskmaster/tasks/tasks.json` for read operations
- Cache task context in memory during session
- Use API calls only for write operations
- Batch updates at logical breakpoints

## **Automatic Workflow**
- Every implementation request → PRD → parse_prd → work on subtasks
- Log progress in subtask details
- Work strictly according to generated subtasks

## **Context Preservation**
- All details in task `details` field
- Research saved to `.taskmaster/docs/research/`
- Structured logging format

See full rules in `.cursor/rules/taskmaster_integration.mdc`
